I don't want anyone seeing
that I'm not perfect.

00:41:42.010 --> 00:41:45.690
I think we all have
those feelings.

00:41:45.690 --> 00:41:49.300
And I think those get in the
way of our resilience and

00:41:49.300 --> 00:41:55.000
adaptiveness, and being able
to course in a much fuller,

00:41:55.000 --> 00:41:58.130
adaptive, resilient,
free world.

